  "detailed_description": "《Pastoral》is a casual simulation, placement of hang-up + oil painting style healing system placement game.<br>The breeze is quiet and the sun is fine! Let's get away from the hustle and bustle and enjoy a moment of idyllic beauty in the game.<br><br><strong>【Game Play】：</strong><br><strong>1, planting vegetables and fruits:</strong> dozens of vegetable fruit trees for you to plant, upgrade;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/efa8699bff256f2ee4b01b6386e566c9.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/efa8699bff256f2ee4b01b6386e566c9.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/efa8699bff256f2ee4b01b6386e566c9.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>2, raising animals: </strong>you can raise different animals in the garden, their output content, range of activities, movement performance will give you a different experience;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/b7e365f23d06fd69bcee1bf5e72da978.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/b7e365f23d06fd69bcee1bf5e72da978.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/b7e365f23d06fd69bcee1bf5e72da978.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3, recruit farmers:</strong> they will automatically help to harvest vegetables and fruits; They can also be equipped with farm tools to improve their work efficiency; The farmers are tired from their work and need a rest. Don't disturb them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/71875aa6e706f3d9b100d280dbfabf51.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/71875aa6e706f3d9b100d280dbfabf51.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/71875aa6e706f3d9b100d280dbfabf51.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4, garden decoration: </strong>you can plant flowers in the garden, mushrooms, sunflowers, lotus, reed, etc., dozens of different kinds of flowers and plants to enrich your garden scenery;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ad738de4532ef503b774fb58ebf18781.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ad738de4532ef503b774fb58ebf18781.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ad738de4532ef503b774fb58ebf18781.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>5, place buildings:</strong> fences can resist monsters to steal vegetables and fruits, build nests for animals can make small animals grow faster, scarecrows can drive away crows...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/1c88e452e0b250743a51446fe620b257.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/1c88e452e0b250743a51446fe620b257.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/1c88e452e0b250743a51446fe620b257.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>6, learn science and technology: </strong>as the level rises, you can aquaculture, fish dock, aircraft automatic fertilization, etc., so that your garden becomes automated, waiting for harvest;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/9170ae91280ba824b1cd00f84c8b4cee.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/9170ae91280ba824b1cd00f84c8b4cee.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/9170ae91280ba824b1cd00f84c8b4cee.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>7, small games:</strong> catch butterflies, whack-a-mole, drive away monsters, tidy up the countryside, repair damaged fences and buildings, fish farming, tree blessing and other daily care!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ac20e5a454a3dc3aa3a07e2460e6746a.poster.avif?t=1699854577\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ac20e5a454a3dc3aa3a07e2460e6746a.webm?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602550/extras/ac20e5a454a3dc3aa3a07e2460e6746a.mp4?t=1699854577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
